<h2>Usage</h2>

<p>
Add the following configuration in your application :

<pre>
{plumber, [
  {memory_threshold, 10000000000}, # bytes
  {memory_check_interval, 5}       # minute
]},
</pre>

Then start the <tt>plumber</tt> application.
</p>

